^ "Biographies". permal.com. 
^ Legg Mason closes on $800M deal. Baltimore Daily Record, November 4, 2005
^ Legg Mason, Inc. (13 March 2013). "Legg Mason and Permal Complete Acquisition of Fauchier Partners". prnewswire.com. 
^ Kozlowski, Rob (2016-09-08). "University of Maine sticks with EnTrustPermal following merger". Pensions & Investments. Retrieved 2017-03-22. 
^ Kozlowski, Rob (2016-09-08). "University of Maine sticks with EnTrustPermal following merger". Pensions & Investments. Retrieved 2017-01-06. 



